### Volunteer Matching API Test Examples
### Run these with REST Client extension in VS Code

### 1. Login (get JWT token first)
# @name login
POST http://localhost:8787/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 2. Match Volunteers for Single Task
POST http://localhost:8787/api/ai/match-volunteers
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

{
  "task": {
    "location": { "lat": 19.076, "lng": 72.877 },
    "needs": ["medical", "emergency_response"],
    "priority_score": 95
  },
  "volunteers": [
    {
      "name": "Dr. Priya Sharma",
      "location": { "lat": 19.076, "lng": 72.877 },
      "skills": ["medical", "emergency_response"],
      "availability": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Rahul Patel",
      "location": { "lat": 19.1, "lng": 72.9 },
      "skills": ["logistics", "transport"],
      "availability": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Anita Desai",
      "location": { "lat": 18.9, "lng": 72.8 },
      "skills": ["medical", "counseling"],
      "availability": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Sunita Rao",
      "location": { "lat": 19.07, "lng": 72.87 },
      "skills": ["medical", "food", "logistics"],
      "availability": true
    }
  ],
  "topN": 3
}

### 3. Match with String Locations
POST http://localhost:8787/api/ai/match-volunteers
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

{
  "task": {
    "location": "Mumbai",
    "needs": ["food", "shelter"],
    "priority_score": 70
  },
  "volunteers": [
    {
      "name": "Vikram Mehta",
      "location": "Mumbai",
      "skills": ["food", "shelter"],
      "availability": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Rahul Patel",
      "location": "Mumbai Central",
      "skills": ["logistics"],
      "availability": true
    }
  ],
  "topN": 3
}

### 4. Batch Match Multiple Tasks
POST http://localhost:8787/api/ai/match-batch
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

{
  "tasks": [
    {
      "location": { "lat": 19.076, "lng": 72.877 },
      "needs": ["medical", "emergency_response"],
      "priority_score": 95
    },
    {
      "location": { "lat": 19.076, "lng": 72.877 },
      "needs": ["food", "shelter"],
      "priority_score": 70
    },
    {
      "location": { "lat": 19.5, "lng": 73.0 },
      "needs": ["medical"],
      "priority_score": 85
    }
  ],
  "volunteers": [
    {
      "name": "Dr. Priya Sharma",
      "location": { "lat": 19.076, "lng": 72.877 },
      "skills": ["medical", "emergency_response"],
      "availability": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Rahul Patel",
      "location": { "lat": 19.1, "lng": 72.9 },
      "skills": ["logistics", "transport"],
      "availability": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Sunita Rao",
      "location": { "lat": 19.07, "lng": 72.87 },
      "skills": ["medical", "food", "logistics"],
      "availability": true
    }
  ],
  "topN": 3
}

### 5. Calculate Match Score (Single Pair)
POST http://localhost:8787/api/ai/match-score
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

{
  "volunteer": {
    "name": "Dr. Priya Sharma",
    "location": { "lat": 19.076, "lng": 72.877 },
    "skills": ["medical", "emergency_response"],
    "availability": true
  },
  "task": {
    "location": { "lat": 19.076, "lng": 72.877 },
    "needs": ["medical", "emergency_response"],
    "priority_score": 95
  }
}

### 6. Match Score - Poor Match
POST http://localhost:8787/api/ai/match-score
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

{
  "volunteer": {
    "name": "Rahul Patel",
    "location": { "lat": 19.1, "lng": 72.9 },
    "skills": ["logistics", "transport"],
    "availability": true
  },
  "task": {
    "location": { "lat": 19.076, "lng": 72.877 },
    "needs": ["medical"],
    "priority_score": 95
  }
}

### 7. Error Case - No Volunteers
POST http://localhost:8787/api/ai/match-volunteers
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

{
  "task": {
    "location": "Mumbai",
    "needs": ["medical"],
    "priority_score": 95
  },
  "volunteers": []
}

### 8. Error Case - Not Available
POST http://localhost:8787/api/ai/match-score
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.token}}

{
  "volunteer": {
    "name": "Test Volunteer",
    "location": "Mumbai",
    "skills": ["medical"],
    "availability": false
  },
  "task": {
    "location": "Mumbai",
    "needs": ["medical"],
    "priority_score": 95
  }
}
